{"id": 2366, "genre": 1001, "title": "为人父母这件事，你觉得要提前准备好应对哪些考验？", "description": "虽然很多想了也不意味着全都应付得来，但总比不想要好很多。（图片来自：视觉中国©️Vetta）", "record_count": 1938, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180523101011fPnFKxGBcIehv6RA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-19T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 299278, "content": "尊重孩子的决定吧，不给孩子规定要走的路。", "image": null, "praise_count": 98, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1418236}, {"id": 299279, "content": "耐心最重要了 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446099}, {"id": 299281, "content": "能把伴侣和自己放在第一位，不是为了孩子而活", "image": null, "praise_count": 301, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381263}, {"id": 299282, "content": "做好负责任的准备。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446114}, {"id": 299284, "content": "要知道自己都还只是身体长大而心智比匹配的“大”人\n尊重与包容孩子这个智慧还未成长起来的个体\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989247}, {"id": 299285, "content": "我还是个孩子啊。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720773}, {"id": 299287, "content": "钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 248, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1376745}, {"id": 299288, "content": "有能力有责任去给孩子一个自由生长的环境。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 912547}, {"id": 299290, "content": "教育究竟是什么，以及如何应对洗脑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718997}, {"id": 299291, "content": "提前要准备好的太多了，好吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386899}, {"id": 299294, "content": "准备好套套吧………生个屁……", "image": null, "praise_count": 92, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446151}, {"id": 299295, "content": "衣食无忧的环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445678}, {"id": 300319, "content": "自己先长大，再教育孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451879}, {"id": 299296, "content": "毫无疑问，应该准备很多钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000871}, {"id": 300832, "content": "准备和美好生活说拜拜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454231}, {"id": 299297, "content": "不离婚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 546278}, {"id": 299298, "content": "我和我们是有区别的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429418}, {"id": 307234, "content": "经济上到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475464}, {"id": 299301, "content": "爱孩子的同时要爱自己，要让孩子知道做父母的辛苦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446183}, {"id": 299304, "content": "如何不将自己身上的性格缺点影响到孩子身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 67, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75414}, {"id": 299306, "content": "要明白孩子不是你的所有物 总有一天会离开你 不要为了孩子而活 也不要让孩子为了你而活", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1398454}, {"id": 299308, "content": "希望所有父母都能意识到①自己和自己的孩子都不是完美的，不要老护短②身为父母就负起所有教育和养育孩子的责任和实践行动，不要推给老人和老师\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1424073}, {"id": 299309, "content": "首先得先喜欢小孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228461}, {"id": 299310, "content": "你就是你孩子的世界观", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212802}, {"id": 299311, "content": "做好把幼儿园、小学、中学再上一遍的准备", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206184}, {"id": 299317, "content": "如果自己还对生活抱有太多疑惑不解，经常性力有未逮，就别想着传宗接代或者养个孩子做宠物。淦临娘。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367473}, {"id": 299318, "content": "被爱子心冲昏头脑，不管对错，护着自己的孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1320043}, {"id": 299319, "content": "把伴侣放在第一位", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382738}, {"id": 299322, "content": "不能养的太盛~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 299323, "content": "如何与孩子共同成长", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446307}, {"id": 299324, "content": "在教小朋友各种知识上各种早教班之前先教会小朋友礼貌待人和正确的行为准则。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304619}, {"id": 299326, "content": "一直一直爱宝宝\n无论发生了什么，不要放弃他/她", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446344}, {"id": 299327, "content": "怎样做孩子正确的榜样才能让宝宝有礼貌有涵养有素质有能力的健康快乐幸福的成长……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031008}, {"id": 299329, "content": "怎么在孩子不懂事的时候教育ta？不想粗暴动手但是感觉不知道其他的办法啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550736}, {"id": 299330, "content": "与人相处，让人舒服即可", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1407374}, {"id": 299331, "content": "不要把自己想做没做的事全寄托在孩子身上让他去完成", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446392}, {"id": 299335, "content": "如何杜绝养儿防老的心理，自己努力做好自己的生活规划，有温情可以享受，同时保持孩子的独立性，并不是自己的附属物。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354705}, {"id": 299336, "content": "不了，我自己还是个娃呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391402}, {"id": 300873, "content": "双方都懂什么是责任 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1454512}, {"id": 299595, "content": "孩子长大，有一天会离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015564}, {"id": 299342, "content": "自己先活明白", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 303703, "content": "孩子有一天质问：问什么生我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009175}, {"id": 299364, "content": "如何培养孩子的审美能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427396}, {"id": 299365, "content": "言传身教\n想把《杀死一只知更鸟》推荐给所有家长。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1404966}, {"id": 299366, "content": "不总是强调自己的付出，并试图从孩子身上索取回来", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062772}, {"id": 299367, "content": "不把自身的生活压力施于孩子身上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062772}, {"id": 299368, "content": "学区房", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585058}, {"id": 299369, "content": "子不孝 父之过", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438927}, {"id": 299370, "content": "一定要学会自我保护", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431996}, {"id": 299371, "content": "如何教育孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445955}]}